OL,3,CWhat next for Iranian regime if its
OL,4,CSupreme Leader is killed?
OL,6,FProblem is, what the clerics and
OL,7,Fscholars who drafted the constitution
OL,8,Fdid not meaningfully contemplate was
OL,9,Fthat the Leader might not fall alone,
OL,10,Fbut alongside the very officials
OL,11,Fdesignated to organise his replacement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
