OL,3,CWhat next for Iranian regime if its
OL,4,CSupreme Leader is killed?
OL,6,FThat possibility no longer feels
OL,7,Ftheoretical. "The strategic objectives
OL,8,Fshould now be clear to you... This
OL,9,Fisn't about any one person. We have
OL,10,Fbeen looking at figures central to the
OL,11,Fregime's governance," a senior Israeli
OL,12,Fofficial with direct knowledge of the
OL,13,Fintelligence discussions told ITV
OL,14,FNews, speaking on condition of
OL,15,Fanonymity, confirming that its
OL,16,Foperation in Iran is aimed not just at
OL,17,Fmilitary targets - or even one man,
OL,18,Fbut the entire mechanism behind him.
OL,26,@oD@NOUsD@UO]
