OL,3,CWhat next for Iranian regime if its
OL,4,CSupreme Leader is killed?
OL,6,FIran's Supreme Leader, Ayatollah Ali
OL,7,FKhamenei ` who has ruled since 1989
OL,8,Fand retains final authority over war,
OL,9,Fpeace, and national security ` is
OL,10,Fstill alive, "as far as I know," the
OL,11,Fcountry's foreign minister said in an
OL,12,Finterview with NBC News on Saturday
OL,13,Fmorning. The caveat there is subtle,
OL,14,Fbut revealing.
OL,26,@rD@NOUrD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
