OL,3,CWhat next for Iranian regime if its
OL,4,CSupreme Leader is killed?
OL,6,FThe Iranian President, Masoud
OL,7,FPezeshkian ` one of the three men
OL,8,Fdesignated under Article 111 to assume
OL,9,Fthe Leader's powers if he were removed
OL,10,F` is also, according to Iranian state
OL,11,Ftelevision, "safe and sound, and has
OL,12,Fno problems." But continuity,
OL,13,Fsuddenly, is something to be asserted,
OL,14,Fnot assumed.
OL,26,@sD@MOUtD@MO]
