OL,3,CWhat next for Iranian regime if its
OL,4,CSupreme Leader is killed?
OL,6,FThe Islamic Republic was engineered to
OL,7,Fsurvive assassination. Its founders
OL,8,Fhad built succession into its
OL,9,Ffoundations. What they did not
OL,10,Fanticipate was an adversary seeking to
OL,11,Fdisrupt succession itself. And that's
OL,12,Fwhat's happening right now.
OL,14,FThe hope, among Israeli and American
OL,15,Fpolicymakers, is that such disruption
OL,16,Fwill create the conditions for
OL,17,Finternal collapse ` that the removal
OL,18,Fnot only of the Leader but of those
OL,19,Fpositioned to replace him might
OL,20,Fproduce not continuity, but rupture -
OL,21,Fan uprising.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
