OL,3,CWhat next for Iranian regime if its
OL,4,CSupreme Leader is killed?
OL,6,FMany of America's allies in the region
OL,7,Fhave feared the risks of that strategy
OL,8,F- their resistance made clear in
OL,9,Fconversations with ITV News over the
OL,10,Flast month. Some have balanced quiet
OL,11,Fhostility towards Iran with caution
OL,12,Fabout the consequences of its
OL,13,Fcollapse. They feared escalation more
OL,14,Fthan they desired resolution.
OL,16,FOman, an intermediary between Tehran
OL,17,Fand Washington, expressed alarm this
OL,18,Fmorning. "I am dismayed," its foreign
OL,19,Fminister said of the US and Israeli
OL,20,Foperation. "I urge the United States
OL,21,Fnot to get sucked in further."
OL,26,@zD@JOUzD@YO]|D@LOU}D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
