OL,3,CWhat next for Iranian regime if its
OL,4,CSupreme Leader is killed?
OL,6,FBut the events that followed - Iran's
OL,7,Fresponse - might have reshaped the
OL,8,Fcalculations of some Middle Eastern
OL,9,Fcountries. Attacking US bases in the
OL,10,Fregion is one thing, but explosions in
OL,11,Fresidential areas are quite different.
OL,12,FSaudi officials have condemned Iran's
OL,13,Factions on its territory today as
OL,14,F"unprovoked" and a violation of their
OL,15,Fsovereignty.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
