OL,3,CWhat next for Iranian regime if its
OL,4,CSupreme Leader is killed?
OL,6,FSenior officials in several Gulf
OL,7,Fcountries told ITV News of their
OL,8,Fgrowing sense of shared exposure `
OL,9,Fthat Iran's willingness to strike
OL,10,Fbeyond its borders might alter their
OL,11,Fperception of the US and Israeli
OL,12,Foperation. "We are well past the form
OL,13,Fof de-escalation we had wanted" said
OL,14,Fone.
OL,26,@tD@LOUuD@_O]
