OL,3,CWhat next for Iranian regime if its
OL,4,CSupreme Leader is killed?
OL,6,FOne result has been an acceleration of
OL,7,Fcoordination between states whose
OL,8,Frelations have, at times, been
OL,9,Fstrained. Saudi and Emirati officials
OL,10,Fare now consulting closely, their
OL,11,Fstrategic outlook converging around a
OL,12,Fcommon question: how to avoid
OL,13,Fescalation and how to shape what comes
OL,14,Fafter it.
OL,16,FThe coming days will test the
OL,17,Fcontingency Article 111 was written to
OL,18,Fcontain. It won't just be events in
OL,19,FTehran, but the responses in Riyadh,
OL,20,FAbu Dhabi and Doha that will be
OL,21,Fconsequential.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
